name: Crispy Baked Brussels Sprouts Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200Â°C. Trim bases of sprouts and halve lengthways. Toss with oil and garlic. Combine breadcrumbs, parmesan and paprika in a bowl. Add sprouts and toss to coat. Spread on tray in a single layer. Bake for 10 minutes, toss, and bake for a further 8-10 minutes or until crisp and golden.
